<L>__{interior pool hall. day}
<A>__{the events in the pool hall, as described by begbie. begbie and tommy are playing pool. begbie is playing like a wizard. tommy looks defeated. lining up for the final ball, begbie is distracted by a large hard man standing at the bar staring at him. begbie stands up and walks slowly towards the hard man. they stand, eye to eye, for a moment. begbie swings the pool cue slowly into his palm. the hard man turns and leaves. begbie drinks the hard man's pint, then pots the black with a brilliant shot.}
